Package administration.daos

Interface IGenericDao<T>


  • public interface IGenericDao<T>
    Created by Max. Combined Interface for all of our Dao classes Completely hides all the JPA/Database related stuff. Always use this interface as the reference type wherever you need to use the Dao!
